<div class="content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <div class="search-result-box card-box">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
              <h1>Publicações</h1>
              <div class="pt-3 pb-4">
                <div class="input-group">
                  <input type="text" id="" name="" class="form-control" value="Admin Dashboard">
                  <div class="input-group-append">
                    <button type="button" class="btn waves-effect waves-light btn-custom"><i class="fa fa-search mr-1"></i> Search</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tab-content">
            <div class="tab-pane active" id="home">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <%= link_to 'Nova publicação', new_publication_path, class: "btn btn-primary mb-3" %>
                  <% @publications.each do | publication | %>
                    <div class="search-item mb-3">
                      <h6 class="mb-1">
                        <%= link_to publication.title, publication_path(publication) %>
                        <span class="small">
                          <%= publication.year %>
                        </span>
                      </h6>
                      <p>
                        <%= publication.publication_type %>
                      </p>
                      <div class="font-13 text-success mb-3">
                        <% publication.authors.each do |author| %>
                          <%= link_to author.name, author_path(author) %>
                        <% end %>
                        <%# Authors %>
                      </div>
                      <p class="mb-0 text-muted">
                        Dolor posuere proin blandit accumsan senectus netus nullam curae, ornare laoreet adipiscing luctus mauris adipiscing pretium eget fermentum, tristique lobortis est ut metus lobortis tortor tincidunt himenaeos habitant quis dictumst proin odio sagittis purus mi, nec taciti vestibulum quis in sit varius lorem sit metus mi.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
